description: The investment objective of the FT Vest Gold Strategy Quarterly Buffer ETF (the "Fund") is to seek to provide investors with returns (before fees and expenses) that match the price return of the SPDR Gold Trust (the "Underlying ETF"), up to a predetermined upside cap of 8.89% while providing a buffer (before fees and expenses) against Underlying ETF losses between -5% and -15% over the period from June 2, 2025 to August 29, 2025.
name: FT Vest Gold Strategy Quarterly Buffer ETF
